under just about any lighting condition and is also responsive to the touch. The device comes preloaded with street maps of the United States, Canada and Puerto Rico. From a personal security standpoint, we particularly appreciate the “Where Am I” emergency locator feature which instantly tells you your current location, nearest address and intersection, as well as providing directions to the nearest emergency services.","As with other contemporary devices, the Nuvi 255W provides both written and audible turn by turn driving directions but it also features text to speech which pronounces the names of the street you’ll be turning on. For example, it will say, “Turn left on Garden Avenue” rather that the more generic “Turn left in 50 yards.” This seemingly minor difference greatly reduces the driver’s inclination to glance at the screen for details rather than watching traffic.","On the downside, the 255W doesn’t allow for excluding certain streets from the route list as many comparable devices do.","The Garmin Nuvi 255W comes with an assortment of functions which aren’t related to navigation but can be of benefit. They include a picture viewer, a world clock with time zones, currency and measurement converters, and a calculator.<br/> "]},"id":"00986772-5b53-4956-89a4-96fb45b41d6a","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_44963","url":"/garmin-nuvi-255w-45794-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"suzanne-humphries","url":"/author/suzanne-humphries","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Suzanne Humphries","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"5Cbzn8X4VHCDchbqEBVidP","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2009-03-25T06:00:00Z","datePublished":"2009-03-25T06:00:00Z","name":"Garmin Nuvi 255W Nuvi 255W","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from viewing as part of this site because it has been discontinued.","review":{"rating":21,"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"stra